    "causal_summary": "sk-code is the single public code skill that routes a request to one of five code modes (implement, quality, debug, verify, review) by workflowMode through mode-registry.json over a shared surface-detection router. The shared router centralizes WEBFLOW, OPENCODE, and MOTION_DEV identity and precedence, while each mode packet owns its own workflow contract and tool surface so the advisor sees exactly one code identity.",
